Key Match Events: Sadio Mane scored a 96th-minute winner for Senegal against Malawi
Miscellaneous Highlights: Ghana are in serious danger of missing out after a surprise loss to Sudan
Others: Senegal had 30 attempts at goal but it took until the final seconds for Mane to seal victory
Democratic Republic of Congo qualified following a 2-0 victory in Tanzania
Coach Avram Grant's Zambia claimed an important 1-0 win over Chad
Gabon are also on course after a 2-0 win over Lesotho in neutral Durban
Hosts Morocco, Cameroon and Algeria are the other teams already in the finals line-up
